thread.title: BRIEF-Shenzhou Yiqiao Information Service sees FY 2017 net profit to be 50 mln yuan to 75 mln yuan

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Shenzhou Yiqiao Information Service sees FY 2017 net profit to be 50 mln yuan to 75 mln yuan

organizations.name: shenzhou yiqiao information service co ltd

text:
Jan 29(Reuters) - Shenzhou Yiqiao Information Service Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to be 50 million yuan to 75 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 45.8 million yuan
* The reasons for the forecast are assets reconstruction and investment on internet service business as well as unload of other company's stock Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/JzBqQc Further company coverage: (Beijing Headline News)
